sequenceDiagram
    participant browser
    participant server

    Note right of browser: User types a note into the text field

    Note right of browser: User clicks "Save" button\nForm submit event is triggered

    browser->>server: POST https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/new_note\n(Form data)
    activate server

    Note right of server: Server saves the new note\ninto memory/database

    server-->>browser: HTTP 302 Redirect to /exampleapp/notes
    deactivate server

    browser->>server: GET https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/notes
    activate server
    server-->>browser: Updated HTML page (including new note)
    deactivate server

    browser->>server: GET main.css
    server-->>browser: CSS file

    browser->>server: GET main.js
    server-->>browser: JavaScript file

    browser->>server: GET data.json
    server-->>browser: Updated notes JSON

